               Transported for Fourteen years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>GARRAD - <rs id="t18320216-176-verdict993" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320216-176-verdict993" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 30.</p>
               <p>SPARKS - <rs id="t18320216-176-verdict994" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320216-176-verdict994" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 27.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18320216-176-punish995" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18320216-176-punish995" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
